Ty Franck of @JamesSACorey and @weschatham are teaming up to bring you The Expanse Aftershow. Tune in weekly after each episode as Ty & That Guy dive into the development, behind-the-scenes, and easter eggs of Season 5, starting 12/16. 

Pants optional. #expants
